We have found that the vast majority of companies now export outside Europe and focus on countries that are modernizing and growing while states in the EU are stagnant.
They wish that new trade links with countries such as China, India and Brazil would be favoured by the government side, rather than dwelling on the long and exhausting process of reforming the obscure EU institutions.
